PN,46901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FTwo men who ran a people smuggling
OL,7,Foperation from Caerphilly to move
OL,8,Fhundreds of migrants into Europe have
OL,9,Fboth been sentenced to 19 years in
OL,10,Fprison each.
OL,12,FDilshad Shamo, 41, and Ali Khdir, 40,
OL,13,Fran a car wash business in the town
OL,14,Fbut a six-month surveillance operation
OL,15,Fby the National Crime Agency (NCA)
OL,16,Funcovered the pair's double lives as
OL,17,Fpeople traffickers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FPolice say Shamo and Khdir facilitated
OL,7,Fthe movement of migrants from Iraq,
OL,8,FIran and Syria into EU countries such
OL,9,Fas Italy, Germany and France. Many of
OL,10,Fthose people are suspected of
OL,11,Feventually arriving in the UK.
OL,13,FMigrants were offered three tiers of
OL,14,Fservice ` the simplest being on foot
OL,15,For via lorry, the next by cargo ships
OL,16,For yachts, and the top tier included
OL,17,Fplane travel.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FOne route by plane from Turkey to
OL,7,FGermany - charged at #13,000 - is
OL,8,Fthought to have been used by at least
OL,9,F11 people during the six-month
OL,10,Foperation.
OL,12,FThe pair are believed to have
OL,13,Ffacilitated at least 142 people to
OL,14,Ftravel by taxi from Croatia to Italy,
OL,15,Ffor a price of around #800 each.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FNCA investigators estimate that at
OL,7,Fleast 409 people were trafficked into
OL,8,FEurope by the men in just the six
OL,9,Fmonths they were being watched by
OL,10,Fofficers. Officers said this was the
OL,11,Flowest estimate and the number of
OL,12,Fpeople successfully trafficked might
OL,13,Fhave numbered more than 600.
OL,15,FNCA Branch Commander Derek Evans said
OL,16,Fthis type of criminality was their
OL,17,Fmain priority, with around 100
OL,18,Foperations currently going on around
OL,19,Fthe UK. 'Single figures' of those are
OL,20,Ffocussing on potential criminality
OL,21,Ftaking place in Wales at the moment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,F"I think this sends a really strong
OL,7,Fmessage," Mr Evans said following the
OL,8,Fsentencing.
OL,10,F"You've got locals looking up to these
OL,11,Fguys as pillars of the community, but
OL,12,Fit was all a facade.
OL,14,F"I hope this will send a message to
OL,15,Fanyone else who is considering this
OL,16,Fkind of crime, that covert operational
OL,17,Fteams like mine and others will find
OL,18,Fyou if you're doing this."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@ZO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FProsecutors said money was lodged with
OL,7,Fan informal system of banking that
OL,8,Fdoes not involve banks, known as
OL,9,FHawala. Agents working for Shamo and
OL,10,FKhdir in Iraq and Istanbul would
OL,11,Farrange and obtain funds from migrants
OL,12,Ftravelling on particular routes.
OL,14,FBefore being taken into custody in
OL,15,FApril 2023, Khdir was recorded by
OL,16,Fhidden microphones in police cars
OL,17,Ftelling Shamo: "Just tell them that we
OL,18,Fare buying and selling cars, just say
OL,19,Fwe do transfer money from our home
OL,20,Fcountry."
OL,26,@yD@POU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FThe men sat through ten days of
OL,7,Fevidence against them during a trial
OL,8,Fin November 2024 before eventually
OL,9,Fchanging their pleas to guilty.
OL,11,FBut neither Shamo and Khdir accepted
OL,12,Fthat their role in the conspiracy was
OL,13,Fas important as made out by police.
OL,14,FThey said they were merely middle-men
OL,15,Fwho facilitated the movement of a
OL,16,Fsmall number of migrants and claimed
OL,17,Fthey did not profit from their
OL,18,Factivities.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FHowever using listening devices in
OL,7,Ftheir cars and place of work, police
OL,8,Fintercepted thousands of messages and
OL,9,Fconversations involving the pair that
OL,10,Funcovered their repeated lies.
OL,12,FShamo and Khdir used WhatsApp to
OL,13,Fcommunicate with people smugglers
OL,14,Facross Europe. Once a deposit was
OL,15,Fobtained, they would receive an 'OK'
OL,16,Ffor migrants to be moved by a
OL,17,Fspecified route or timeframe.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FThey also used messaging and social
OL,7,Fmedia apps to provide videos from
OL,8,Fpeople who had already taken the
OL,9,Fjourney so they could advertise their
OL,10,Froutes. In one video, a family
OL,11,Ftravelling by plane details the route
OL,12,Fand states, "we are very happy... this
OL,13,Fis the visa, may god bless him, we are
OL,14,Freally happy."
OL,16,FIn another, a man travelling by HGV
OL,17,Ftells the camera: "Lorry route
OL,18,Fagreement, crossing agreement with the
OL,19,Fknowledge of the driver. Here we have
OL,20,Fmen, women and children. Thank god the
OL,21,Froute was easy and good."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FShamo was asked by the prosecution's
OL,7,Fbarrister Sarah Gaunt whether he and
OL,8,FKhdir did any of the trafficking to
OL,9,Fmake money for themselves.
OL,11,F"If I was working in this type of job,
OL,12,FI would have my Ferrari, I would have
OL,13,Fmy palace," he said.
OL,15,F"If I was doing this, why would I work
OL,16,Fin a carwash and have 1000 in my
OL,17,Faccount?"
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@AOUyD@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FHowever the prosecution said a lack of
OL,7,Ffinancial evidence was common in cases
OL,8,Fsuch as these, as informal banking
OL,9,Fthrough the Hawala system was often
OL,10,Funtraceable.
OL,12,FA special hearing at Cardiff Crown
OL,13,FCourt in April 2026 heard directly
OL,14,Ffrom both men from the witness box.
OL,15,FShamo said their activities abroad
OL,16,Fbegan when they tried to smuggle a
OL,17,Ffamily member of Khdir's into Europe
OL,18,Ffrom their home in Kurdistan, via
OL,19,FIstanbul.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FIn evidence, Shamo and Khdir's defence
OL,7,Fbarristers argued the thousands of
OL,8,Fmessages about logistics and planning
OL,9,Ffor people smuggling activities were
OL,10,Fan attempt to give the pair
OL,11,Fcredibility and status with criminal
OL,12,Foperators abroad.
OL,14,FThe men claimed they thought this
OL,15,Fwould give the people smugglers they
OL,16,Fwere dealing with a fear of potential
OL,17,Fretribution if they hurt Khdir's
OL,18,Ffamily as they attempted to enter the
OL,19,FEU.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FBut in judgement, Her Honour Judge
OL,7,FLloyd-Clarke pointed to evidence
OL,8,Fgathered covertly by police of a
OL,9,Fconversation between Shamo and his
OL,10,Fwife in 2023 where he told her he had
OL,11,Fpeople working for him all over Europe.
OL,13,F"All agents are under my control,
OL,14,Fincluding those in Bosnia, Serbia,
OL,15,FTurkey, Italy, and Slovenia," he told
OL,16,Fher during a private conversation in
OL,17,Fhis car in Caerphilly.
OL,19,F"We have cars and if they cross the
OL,20,Fborder into Turkey, I will manage the
OL,21,Frest."
OL,26,@uD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FThe Judge said there would be no need
OL,7,Fto pretend to his wife that he was a
OL,8,Fpeople smuggler.
OL,10,FA National Crime Agency investigator
OL,11,Fwho gave evidence in court said they
OL,12,Fhad estimated that more than #1.8
OL,13,Fmillion had been spent by people in
OL,14,Freturn for being trafficked across
OL,15,FEuropean borders.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46915
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FWhile impossible to trace how much of
OL,7,Fthat ended up in Shamo and Khdir's
OL,8,Fpersonal possession, Her Honour Judge
OL,9,FLloyd-Clarke was clear in her
OL,10,Fjudgement that this was a business run
OL,11,Fto make profit for the defendants.
OL,13,FAfter assessing all the evidence in
OL,14,Fthe case, the Judge told the court: "I
OL,15,Fam sure that the prosecution has
OL,16,Fproved that the defendants were
OL,17,Forganised, they were motivated by
OL,18,Ffinancial gain, and the conspiracy
OL,19,Fsuccessfully moved hundreds of
OL,20,Fmigrants".
OL,26,@vD@eOU|D@IO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FShe said the pair were well
OL,7,Festablished and could have moved
OL,8,Fhundreds more people had they not been
OL,9,Farrested.
OL,11,FOn sentencing, Her Honour Judge Lloyd-
OL,12,FClarke said this was "sophisticated
OL,13,Foffending".
OL,26,@tD@VOUuD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FShe said they both acted primarily for
OL,7,Ffinancial gain, and their crimes were
OL,8,Faggravated by the fact they were
OL,9,Ffacilitating the smuggling very
OL,10,Fregularly and because they helped
OL,11,Fpeople who were vulnerable to take
OL,12,Frisks by travelling on the routes they
OL,13,Fdetermined.
OL,15,FThe Judge told both men they would
OL,16,Fserve a minimum of 7 and a half years
OL,17,Fof their sentences behind bars before
OL,18,Fthey would be eligible for parole.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G17/19
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46918
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776258665
OL,3,CMen who smuggled hundreds of people
OL,4,Cinto Europe from car wash jailed
OL,6,FNCA Branch Commander Derek Evans said
OL,7,Finvestigators had not been able to
OL,8,Ftrace any of the individuals who they
OL,9,Fbelieve were smuggled into Europe, and
OL,10,Ftherefore do not know if any of those
OL,11,Fmigrants had a history of offending in
OL,12,Ftheir origin countries.
OL,14,FTheir investigation was supported by
OL,15,FGwent Police. Detective Sergeant Simon
OL,16,FThomas from that force said: "This
OL,17,Fcase demonstrates clearly how agencies
OL,18,Fcan work together successfully to
OL,19,Fsupport the victims and target the
OL,20,Fcriminals behind the exploitation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G18/19
